**License Model**

This project follows an "Open Core + Commercial Extension" dual model:

- **Open Source Core**: Protocol definitions, architecture documentation, core engine
  implementation, plugin framework, and UI bridge protocol are licensed under MIT.
- **Commercial Extensions**: Advanced strategy libraries, professional data services,
  enterprise-grade risk management, multi-account management, and other premium
  features may be offered under separate commercial licenses.

Contributors to the open source core retain copyright to their contributions.
Commercial extensions are separate from the open source core and are not subject
to this MIT license.
